{"tid":2079553,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登音樂台]利物浦奪冠之歌-奪冠","createTime":"2020-06-26T00:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T13:42:31.000Z","uid":5655,"like":9,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9b97606ee2102a3d9f4d6a2e26ab07a00d8a3db9","tid":2079553,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T00:44:11.000Z","msg":"原曲:單車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於終於比我等到<br />\n一切一切也都是好像發夢<br />\n高普這麼偉大 我們感覺得到<br />\n今次奪冠的愛有多好<br />\n英超捧杯今次實在接觸到<br />\n難忘棒杯的一刻 我們一起的擁抱<br />\n<br />\n文尼沙拉 高普神軒 奪冠奇蹟 好想多次<br />\n如孩兒能伏於爸爸的肩膊 我係利迷<br />\n三十年來 等左好耐 古仔功勞不可推卸<br />\n任病毒再冷酷 想起這奪冠 還有什麼可輸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AfPUiV-jamA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAfPUiV-jamA&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Sr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=80bfc648\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AfPUiV-jamA</a>"},{"pid":"a8428fb07c71f37b8239b7ccd037341fd1bf32c5","tid":2079553,"uid":129348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T00:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4o09EQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4o09EQ.jpg&h=2757c254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求 反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書"},{"pid":"d05a8500e2f8905e5a145dca2db2d65384978bfc","tid":2079553,"uid":320814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"邊間教會"},{"pid":"18642cccc759ad38a1a9ee5b753a380dc9cfb493","tid":2079553,"uid":230544,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T00:53:04.000Z","msg":"哇屌<br />\n明白咁難拎到第一次冠<br />\n係應該打飛機<br />\n可以理解<br />\n<br />\n但咁撚難聽 詞又唔岩 <br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af808dbb956603d6f7b3a1bdef830fad8e59837","tid":2079553,"uid":356101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T00:56: